  "text": "Antibodies to the following proteins were utilised in this study: SOX9 (Millipore, #AB5535); AMH (Santa Cruz, #sc28912); FOXL2 (a kind gift from Dagmar Wilhelm and Peter Koopman [CITATION_1] ); SRY (a kind gift from Makoto Tachibana, Kyoto University [CITATION_2] ); Cell Signaling antibodies -p38 MAPK (CST9212), phospho-p38 MAPK (CST9215), ERK (CST9102) and phospho-ERK (CST4377); 12G10 alpha-tubulin (Developmental Studies Hybridoma Bank, University of Iowa). Immunostaining was performed on sectioned, paraffin wax-embedded tissue from two independent gonad samples using the above primary antibodies (1:100) and Alexa Fluor 594 (AMH, SOX9) or 488 (FOXL2, SRY) conjugated secondary antibodies (1:200). Images were captured using a Zeiss 710 multiphoton microscope.",
